727259f-a.title: Queens: Little Neck Parkway - 60th Avenue
727259f-a.text:
Little Neck Parkway, east side, between Sixtieth Ave. (formerly
East Alley Road) and Horace Harding Boulevard, showing the home of
J. Poole in 1873. The realty atlas of 1891 shows ownership in I. Poll.
In 1909 the property belonged to William E. Vanderbilt Jr. The house
does not appear in the Queens Atlas of 1928. This is a set of three
views.
May 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
